/strong><strong>?</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ক. &nbsp;Welcome &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. Welcome &nbsp;Good Bye</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;গ. Good Bye &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. উপরের কোনোটিই নয়</p><p><strong>২৯</strong><strong>।</strong> i<strong>f</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্টটিকে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কিভাবে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>লিখলে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>আউটপুট</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>আসবে</strong><strong>?</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ক. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;if (age &gt; 10) printf(&ldquo; Welcome &rdquo;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; else &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; printf (&ldquo; Good Bye &rdquo;); &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (age &gt; 10) {</p><p>printf(&ldquo; Welcome &rdquo;);</p><p>printf (&ldquo; Good Bye &rdquo;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; } &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; গ. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if (age &gt; 10) {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; printf(&ldquo; Welcome &rdquo;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; printf (&ldquo; Good Bye &rdquo;);</p><p>ঘ. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if স্টেটমেন্টটি সঠিকই আছে।</p><p><strong>৩০</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভাষা</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নিম্নলিখিত</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কাজে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ব্যবহৃত</strong><strong>&nbsp;nq</strong><strong>&ndash;</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ক. &nbsp;ডেটাবেজ নিয়ে কাজ করার জন্য &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;খ. &nbsp;প্রোগ্রাম লেখার জন্য</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;গ. HTML ফাইল তৈরীর জন্য &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. &nbsp;কম্পিউটার চালানোর জন্য</p><p><strong>৩১</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>while</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>লুপ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>এবং</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>do while</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>লুপের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>মধ্যে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>একটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>গুরুত্বপূর্ণ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>পার্থক্য</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হলো</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নিম্নরূপ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>:</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ক. &nbsp;সব কিছু একই রকম থাকলে, while লুপ যদি k বার ঘোরে তবে do while লুপ ঘোরে k-1 বার</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;খ. সব কিছু একই রকম থাকলে, while লুপ যদি k বার ঘোরে তবে do while লুপ ঘোরে k+1 বার</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;গ. while লুপ এবং do while লুপের মধ্যে আসলে কোনো পার্থক্য নাই।</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. condition এর উপর ভিত্তি করে while লুপ একবারো নাও ঘুরতে পারে, কিন্তু condition যাই হোক, do while লুপ অন্তত একবার ঘুরবেই।</p><p><strong>৩২</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>তুমি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>একটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রোগ্রামে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>f1()</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নামের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>একটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ফাংশন</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>main()</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ফাংশনে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ব্যাবহার</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করেছ</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>নিম্নের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোনটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ঘটলে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রোগ্রামটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভাবে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কম্পাইল</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হবে</strong><strong>?</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ক. &nbsp; f1 নামের ফাংশনটি তুমি নিজে নির্ভুল ভাবে লিখছো।</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;খ. &nbsp;f1 নামের ফাংশনটি তুমি নিজে লেখনি কিন্তু শুরুতে সংশ্লিষ্ট হেডার ফাইলটি include করেছ।</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;গ. &nbsp;f1 নামের ফাংশনটিতে তুমি কোনো parameter ব্যবহার করনি।</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. &nbsp;ক এবং খ এর মধ্যে যে কোনো একটি ঘটলে।</p><p><strong>৩৩</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ব্যবহারকারীর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>বয়স</strong><strong>&nbsp;(</strong><strong>age&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভেরিয়েবল</strong><strong>)</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>৩</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>থেকে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>৯</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>এর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>মধ্যে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>না</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>থাকলে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রোগ্রাম</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>return&nbsp;</strong><strong>করবে</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>এ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>জন্য</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নিচের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোন</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>if</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্টটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ক. if (age &lt; 3 | | age &gt; 9) return 0;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;খ. if (age &lt; 3 &amp;&amp; age &gt; 9) return 0;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;গ. if (age &gt; 3 | | age &lt; 9) return 0;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. if (age &gt; 3 &amp;&amp; age &lt; 9) return 0;</p><p><strong>৩৪</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নিচের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>switch &nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্টের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>পর</strong><strong>&nbsp;abc</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভেরিয়েবলের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>মান</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কত</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হবে</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ধরে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নাও</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>switch &nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্টের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>আগে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>abc&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভেরিয়েবলের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>মান</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ছিল</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>২</strong><strong>।</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; switch(abc)</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; case 1:</p><p>abc--;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; break;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; case 2:</p><p>abc++;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; case 3: &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>abc*abc;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; case 4:</p><p>abc+abc;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; break;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; default:</p><p>abc/abc;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>ক. &nbsp;১৮ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. ২</p><p>গ. ১ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. ৪</p><p><strong><strong>৩৫</strong><strong>।</strong> C&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রোগ্রামিং</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভাষায়</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্টগুলো</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হলো</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>i. অ্যাসাইনমেন্ট</p><p>ii. রিলেশনাল</p><p>iii. কন্ট্রোল</p><p><strong>উপরের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোনটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. i ও ii &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. ii ও iii</p><p>গ. i ও iii &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. i, ii ও iii</p><p><strong>নিম্নে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>C&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোডের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>একটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>অংশ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>দেওয়া</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হলো</strong><strong>।</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>এর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>উপর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভিত্তি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>৩৬</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>৩৮</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নং</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রশ্নের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>উত্তর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>দাও</strong><strong>।</strong></p><p>i = 0</p><p>do {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; printf(&ldquo;%d&rdquo;,i);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; i + +;</p><p>} while (i&lt;10)</p><p><strong><strong>৩৬</strong><strong>।&nbsp;</strong>এই</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>অংশে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোন</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ধরনের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্ট</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ব্যবহার</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করা</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হয়নি</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. ইনপুট &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. আউটপুট</p><p>গ. কন্ট্রোল &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. অ্যাসাইনমেন্ট</p><p><strong><strong>৩৭</strong><strong>।</strong> প্রোগ্রামটির</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>এই</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>অংশে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রিন্ট</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হবে</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. 0, 1, ..................... 9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. 1, 2, ..................... 9</p><p>গ. 1, 2, ..................... 10 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. 0, 1, ..................... 10</p><p><strong><strong>৩৮</strong><strong>।</strong> উপরের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>লুপটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কয়বার</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>চলবে</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. 0 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;খ. 1</p><p>গ. 9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. 10</p><p><strong><strong>৩৯</strong><strong>।</strong> কোন</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>লুপ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কন্ট্রোল</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্ট</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কমপক্ষে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>একবার</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>চলবে</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. for &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;খ. if</p><p>গ. do &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. while</p><p><strong><strong>৪০<strong><strong>।</strong></strong></strong> &amp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>চিহ্নটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>C</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রোগ্রামিং</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভাষায়</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নিম্নলিখিতভাবে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ব্যবহৃত</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হতে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>পারে</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>i. Address বের করার জন্য</p><p>ii. লজিক্যাল অপারেটর</p><p>iii. ইনপুট স্টেটমেন্ট</p><p style=\"\"><strong>উপরের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোনটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"\">ক. i ও ii &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. ii ও iii</p><p style=\"\">গ. i ও iii &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. i, ii ও iii</p><p style=\"\"><strong><strong>৪১<strong><strong>।</strong></strong></strong> রিকার্সিভ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ফাংশনের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>বৈশিষ্ট্য</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হলো</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>i. এর যে কোন স্থানে ঐ ফাংশনকে call করবে</p><p>ii. এতে টার্মিনেটিং কন্ডিশন থাকবে</p><p>iii. এতে অবশ্যই ইনপুট স্টেটমেন্ট থাকবে</p><p style=\"\"><strong>উপরের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোনটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"\">ক. i ও ii &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. ii ও iii</p><p style=\"\">গ. i ও iii &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. i, ii ও iii</p><p style=\"\"><strong>নিম্নের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>অনুচ্ছেদের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>উপর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ভিত্তি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>৪২</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>৪৪</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নং</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>প্রশ্নের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>উত্তর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>দাও</strong><strong>।</strong></p><p style=\"\">কোনো একটি গোলকের আয়তন বের করার সূত্র হলো <!--[if !vml]--><!--[endif]-->, যেখানে r দ্বারা গোলকের ব্যাসার্ধ এবং v দ্বারা গোলকের আয়তন বোঝানো হয়। একটি প্রোগ্রাম লেখা হলো যা গোলকের ব্যাসার্ধকে ইনপুট হিসাবে নেওয়া হয় এবং গোলকের আয়তন স্ক্রিনে দেখানো হয়। এই প্রোগ্রামে চলক ও ধ্রুবকের ব্যবহার করা আবশ্যক।</p><p style=\"\"><strong><strong>৪২<strong><strong>।</strong></strong></strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>&pi;&nbsp;</strong><strong>এর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>মান</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ধ্রুবক</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হিসাবে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নির্দেশ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করা</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>যায়</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোন</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>স্টেটমেন্ট</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>এর</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>মাধ্যমে</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"\">ক. const int pi = 3.14; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. int pi = 3.14;</p><p style=\"\">গ. const double pi = 3.14; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. double pi = 3.14;</p><p style=\"\"><strong><strong><strong>৪৩<strong><strong>।</strong></strong></strong></strong> নিম্নের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>কোনটি</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ব্যাসার্ধ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নির্দেশিত</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>চলকের</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>সঠিক</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>নাম</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. 1r &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. #r</p><p style=\"\">গ. r &ndash; 1 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ঘ. উপরের কোনোটি নয়</p><p style=\"\"><strong><strong><strong>৪৪<strong><strong>।</strong></strong></strong></strong> ডেটা</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>টাইপ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>উল্লেখ</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>না</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করে</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>p</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ধ্রুবক</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>ডিক্লেয়ার</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>করার</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>উপায়</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>হলো</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>ক. const pi 3.14 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; খ. #define pi 3.14</p><p>গ. pi = 3.14 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ঘ. pi = 3.14</p><p align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p align=\"center\"><strong><!--[if !vml]-->&nbsp;</strong></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-right: calc(100% - 98% - 0px); width: 98%;\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" width=\"42\">১<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"35\">খ<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"41\">২<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"36\">ঘ<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"42\">৩<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"36\">ক<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"42\">৪<br></td><td style=\"width: 6.3372%;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"36\">ক<br></td><td style=\"width: 7.351%;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"42\">৫<br></td><td style=\"width: 6.3371%;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"36\">ঘ<br></td><td style=\"width: 7.0976%;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"40\">৬<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"61\">গ<br></td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"43\">৭<br></td><td valign=\"top